职场门槛」与社会发展趋势背道而驰。 因此，他建议，「逐步适当放开公务员录用考试‘35 周岁以下’的限制。」这将有利于对全社会就业或者再就业起到示范性作用，有助于解决就业市场上的年龄歧视。上热搜！委员建议放宽 35 岁就业年龄限制"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-416629ea8bce956314c73b2a82572a67_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "111 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647102957"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI2p/b4Iv2qfFJEAMaCTEwNjA3ODAxMCC2yJmvBjAAOIECQAVyCTY0NzEwMjk1N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1709655661.52144", "card_id": "Q_646534103", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价环保题材电视剧《江河日上》?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-9a2997415988b05f487cc8a35647093a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "89 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/646534103"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2p/b4Iv2qfFJEAMaCTEwNTk1MTk1NCD/6oOvBjAAODRABnIJNjQ2NTM0MTAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1709655661.52521", "card_id": "Q_19602183", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15932}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人最重要的能力是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "镜像问题：人最不重要的能力是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": "